snippet.title: Arcade Game: Water Match (1984 Sega)
snippet.description:
A Sports/Track & Field game with multi events similar to Konami's Track & Field series with events such as freestyle swimming, one-man kayaking, four-man canoeing, and Canoeing gates passing. 

Gameplay starts at 00:52.

The controls are jerky and sloppy making this a terrible game. Sega's attempted to compete with Konami's Track & Field series.
